<h6>
<span class="fa fa-bullhorn fa-fw fa-lg"></span><strong>Suspension of in-person K-12 instruction for the remainder of 2019-2020 school year</strong><br>
Per the <a href="https://www.michigan.gov/whitmer/0,9309,7-387-90499_90705-524032--,00.html" target="_blank">Governor's Executive Order</a>, Escuela Avancemos will be closed for the remainder of the 19-20 school year. We are looking forward to returning next year for the 20-21 school year! <br><br><span class="fa fa-cutlery fa-fw fa-lg" style="color:#66ff66"></span><strong>Food Distribution</strong><br>
